Support of KNX functions through innovative colour concept (yellow=lighting, blue=blind, orange=RTC, magenta=scene and white=neutral/no function assigned) or standard illumination red/green. Push switch function: switching / dimming / blind / sending values / scenes etc. For activating heating, ventilation and fan coil actuators. Master/slave configuration. With base-load operation. The fan stage can be switched manually or in automatic mode. Class of temperature controller 1 Contribution to space heating energy efficiency 1,0%. Number of bus subscribers: 2
